channel.title: I can't connect to my address
channel.description: So I've been trying to connect to my IP Address because I hear you can host your website using your IP Address but the thing is, a window pops up asking for my User and Pass and I never recall making one so how do I access it?

item.title: I can't connect to my address

item.description:
